{"tid":1949776,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人股票投資 101 【P/E 的迷思尾篇】","createTime":"2020-03-30T01:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T15:07:00.000Z","uid":125976,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a17c7353968bf41f53151f30e0cf727ed4b2d286","tid":1949776,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T01:50:43.000Z","msg":"前篇：<br />\n窮人股票投資 101（P/E 的迷思）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1947426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1947426</a><br />\n<br />\n窮人股票投資 101 【P/E 的迷思續篇】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949288</a><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n我哋繼續星之屎嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星先生因為做衰咗除夕抽獎網同防疫 app，而家每年得返 $2000 萬政府項目做，覺得灰心意冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢垂頭喪氣行到天橋底，見到本窮狗喺度乞食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGmpZdB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvGmpZdB.jpg&h=0b33e774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n星先生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本窮狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「唉！真係同是天涯淪落人，唔通香城真係 NO IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「咪就係你哋𠵱啲仆街囉！靠識人圍威喂鳩吹就攞到政府 projects 同 funding，令到我哋𠵱啲做實事嘅仙都冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我啱啱先俾人炒撚埋，個老細二世祖嚟，咪又係鳩吹搞個 app，靠關係 cap 完政府錢再請班狗揼。仲要又天馬行空又離地，我哋辛辛苦苦完晒佢啲離地 requirements 搞到 IPO 就炒撚晒我哋，冇天理！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「係咁㗎啦，我最近都好煩，平時接開政府八千萬 projects，而家得返二千萬，我仲諗住 5 年後搞上市，冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「咁係你做啲嘢垃圾嘛，你除咗識黐政府仲識乜？不過唔係完全冇計嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「你有計？我最多教埋你舔共攞 funding 秘技，你要幫吓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「好，就傳授你投行二世祖秘法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n續，要返工揼垃圾，之後喺下面再寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b559f76b7f93c0d7188d7de99093e3f28f5d646","tid":1949776,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T01:54:59.000Z","msg":"正題？"},{"pid":"92c23c24f3912f79d235e435368733f44ca93e6c","tid":1949776,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T01:55:04.000Z","msg":"快啦"},{"pid":"ff143268de847ecbaf1bbea339e68987d3122ad3","tid":1949776,"uid":38662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T01:55:58.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628a35996b65755e6f17682a112ee5529d8160a8","tid":1949776,"uid":68445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T01:59:14.000Z","msg":"尾篇仲以為可以一次追哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf9f64e4c9737b9da34ac1b17430c4d5c0402d6","tid":1949776,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"628a35996b65755e6f17682a112ee5529d8160a8","tid":1949776,"uid":68445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T01:59:14.000Z","msg":"尾篇仲以為可以一次追哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T02:00:13.000Z","msg":"冇計，唔夠時間寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98