nghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我啱啱先俾人炒撚埋，個老細二世祖嚟，咪又係鳩吹搞個 app，靠關係 cap 完政府錢再請班狗揼。仲要又天馬行空又離地，我哋辛辛苦苦完晒佢啲離地 requirements 搞到 IPO 就炒撚晒我哋，冇天理！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「係咁㗎啦，我最近都好煩，平時接開政府八千萬 projects，而家得返二千萬，我仲諗住 5 年後搞上市，冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「咁係你做啲嘢垃圾嘛，你除咗識黐政府仲識乜？不過唔係完全冇計嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「你有計？我最多教埋你舔共攞 funding 秘技，你要幫吓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「好，就傳授你投行二世祖秘法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n續，要返工揼垃圾，之後喺下面再寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T02:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「準備好向大師學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n好，知唔知班投行二世祖睇一間公司最 care 係乜？<br />\n<br />\n佢哋只 care 三樣嘢（講梗一般行業）：<br />\n1. 間公司係咪穩陣年年賺到錢（盈利穩定）<br />\n2. (1) 仲未夠，間公司係咪每年愈賺愈多錢（盈利增長穩定）<br />\n3. 你嘅行業係咪毛利率高 (or 睇純利率都差唔多)<br />\n<br />\n睇星先生你個 case，本來係符合 (1)，但做爛咗兩個 projects 之後屬已經連 (1) 已經唔符合<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「咁點算呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:24:31.000Z","msg":"本窮狗完全 ignore 星先生嘅問題，繼續講落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你知唔知點解企鵝公司可以長期享有咁高嘅 P/E？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我有睇過你之前 lihkg 開 post 講過啦，睇個主席靚唔靚仔嘛，我就唔撚信你真係咁揀股<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0N40qk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0N40qk.jpg&h=cd3afa43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：不過馬生真係幾靚仔喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：好，去返正題，我雖然真係睇主席樣揀股，但你信唔信班投行二世祖一樣咁揀股？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔多信囉，如果唔係佢哋點同啲客解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁即係佢哋有理性啲嘅另一套啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n其實咁嘅，企鵝而家個市咁差都至少有 30 倍 forecast P/E 啦，咁俾得 30 倍 P/E 你梗係有代價啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實俾 30 倍 P/E，個前題就係你要做到至少 30% 盈利增長囉（記住唔係營收增長，係淨利潤呀）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁如果企鵝之後嗰三年都係得 15% 盈利增長，會點？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：好似你間公司咁，遲早俾人洗倉囉，洗到得返 15 倍 P/E 呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---<br />\n其實𠵱度我哋已經學咗一個 concept，叫 PEG (本益成長比)<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">PEG = P/E &divide; 增長率\nPEG &gt; 1 就係開始偏貴\nPEG = 1 就係合理價\nPEG &lt; 1 就係開始抵買</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n不過都係嗰個前題啦，係講梗盈利穩定增長先用得，你一年賺多 30%，第二年又蝕錢蝕 10%，咁計嚟都嘥氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你仲未解答我問題，我公司咁嘅環境點算，唔通我真係白白睇住班投行二世祖洗我倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n續。"},{"pid":"25fe350cdd181cf7315bf9d4a440a17b357d93c7","tid":1949776,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea27912d1f27a52804feba2d212107f202f80f7b","tid":1949776,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"161762cdc3f65aceed2fcac176388a3694f8272f","tid":1949776,"uid":125976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a17c7353968bf41f53151f30e0cf727ed4b2d286","tid":1949776,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T01:50:43.000Z","msg":"前篇：<br />\n窮人股票投資 101（P/E 的迷思）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1947426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1947426</a><br />\n<br />\n窮人股票投資 101 【P/E 的迷思續篇】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949288</a><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n我哋繼續星之屎嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星先生因為做衰咗除夕抽獎網同防疫 app，而家每年得返 $2000 萬政府項目做，覺得灰心意冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢垂頭喪氣行到天橋底，見到本窮狗喺度乞食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGmpZdB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvGmpZdB.jpg&h=0b33e774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n星先生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本窮狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「唉！真係同是天涯淪落人，唔通香城真係 NO IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「咪就係你哋𠵱啲仆街囉！靠識人圍威喂鳩吹就攞到政府 projects 同 funding，令到我哋𠵱啲做實事嘅仙都冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />