faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n續。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：其實要解決你公司盈利大幅倒退嘅問題，得幾種辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：快啲講啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---<br />\n1. 增加營收（開源）<br />\n2. 減少支出（節流）<br />\n3. 撥數做假（吊命）<br />\n---<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌，1, 2 係人都知啦，你又廢噏乜嘢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：1 方面我已經盡力去足柒婆啲酒會，幫佢舔鞋底舔到叮一聲，但連柒婆都話好難做，我嗰兩個 projects 真係做衰咗嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：2 方面我而家已經炒咗一半 code 狗，剩返一半 code 狗一隻揼之前兩隻狗揼嘅嘢，你仲想點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：好，我哋繼續講<br />\n---<br />\n我以你往幾年嚟講，香城政府利益輸送 $8000萬 projects 俾你，你扣除晒狗薪雜費後，純利大約 $2000 萬左右<br />\n<br />\n純利率即係：<br />\n$2000 萬 &divide; $8000 萬 = 25%<br />\n<br />\n咁如果你用（1）增加營收，假設而家香城政俾多 $8000 萬 projects 你做，而你純利率不變，純利即係：<br />\n1.6 億 &times; 25% = $4000 萬<br />\n<br />\n你嘅盈利增長就係增長咗 100%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁既然（1）做唔到，我哋點解會諗（2）？<br />\n<br />\n因為你炒咗一半 code 狗，用之前一隻狗做兩隻狗嘅嘢，咁即係支出減少咗啦，純利率就增加咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假設純利率：<br />\n25% =&gt; 40%<br />\n<br />\n你而家接得香城政府 $2000 萬 projects，好似倒退咗 3/4 咁，但你再計吓：<br />\n$2000 萬 &times; 40% = $800 萬<br />\n<br />\n咁計都係倒退咗 60% 咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁一樣係仆晒街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n續。"},{"pid":"150fbb9a61017f61a29798d4d9bc6200964c3579","tid":1949776,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:26:56.000Z","msg":"成堆二世祖負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4846fc3c439c085c60e669e1e09570ff02f9e011","tid":1949776,"uid":24224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517ee018afc15cb2279146849fc077e579ef9917","tid":1949776,"uid":82381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"大師點睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469e60c036db80ce18417dbdb220f2b8e9b7b1fd","tid":1949776,"uid":125976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"517ee018afc15cb2279146849fc077e579ef9917","tid":1949776,"uid":82381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"大師點睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:32:41.000Z","msg":"24 蚊以下先靚仔，而家四叔好樣衰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWAVosb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWAVosb.jpg&h=f4f76e10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84699a665b355c937cfa3c7a0c8b1c45d9686adf","tid":1949776,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47629bbec44c680b2f62418780ec1aba6c38a03","tid":1949776,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"883c60dbcf885af1dd7aed80b215ca6be1107fd3","tid":1949776,"uid":125976,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3c7f73c69fc55ad6ad09aceb5a54586e8b95511b","tid":1949776,"uid":24224,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"repl