oji\" /><br />\n<br />\n續。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：其實要解決你公司盈利大幅倒退嘅問題，得幾種辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：快啲講啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---<br />\n1. 增加營收（開源）<br />\n2. 減少支出（節流）<br />\n3. 撥數做假（吊命）<br />\n---<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌，1, 2 係人都知啦，你又廢噏乜嘢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：1 方面我已經盡力去足柒婆啲酒會，幫佢舔鞋底舔到叮一聲，但連柒婆都話好難做，我嗰兩個 projects 真係做衰咗嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：2 方面我而家已經炒咗一半 code 狗，剩返一半 code 狗一隻揼之前兩隻狗揼嘅嘢，你仲想點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：好，我哋繼續講<br />\n---<br />\n我以你往幾年嚟講，香城政府利益輸送 $8000萬 projects 俾你，你扣除晒狗薪雜費後，純利大約 $2000 萬左右<br />\n<br />\n純利率即係：<br />\n$2000 萬 &divide; $8000 萬 = 25%<br />\n<br />\n咁如果你用（1）增加營收，假設而家香城政俾多 $8000 萬 projects 你做，而你純利率不變，純利即係：<br />\n1.6 億 &times; 25% = $4000 萬<br />\n<br />\n你嘅盈利增長就係增長咗 100%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁既然（1）做唔到，我哋點解會諗（2）？<br />\n<br />\n因為你炒咗一半 code 狗，用之前一隻狗做兩隻狗嘅嘢，咁即係支出減少咗啦，純利率就增加咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假設純利率：<br />\n25% =&gt; 40%<br />\n<br />\n你而家接得香城政府 $2000 萬 projects，好似倒退咗 3/4 咁，但你再計吓：<br />\n$2000 萬 &times; 40% = $800 萬<br />\n<br />\n咁計都係倒退咗 60% 咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁一樣係仆晒街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n續。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：仲有最後一招嘛，撥前啲數囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你同柒婆講，話因為要做靚盤數，叫佢一次過俾三年 projects 錢，之後幫佢做捉三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係喎，等我返去再幫佢舔吓屄先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n三年盈利：<br />\n$2000 萬 &times; 3 = $6000 萬<br />\n<br />\n再將三年盈利直接撥入今年財報<br />\n<br />\n咁睇起上嚟就好似今年只係賺少咗 $2000 萬<br />\n---<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁下年一樣係仆街㗎啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嗱，情況又唔同喎，起碼你多一年時間慢慢照顧你班主子同搵新客<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：同埋你可以將 2/3 盈利撥到首半年報表，咁預測市盈率咪會好睇啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：乜撚嘢係預測市盈率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n預測市盈率即係用一季 / 半年報表估算未出嘅全年報表盈利，再計返個 P/E 出嚟<br />\n---<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：而家你將 $6000 萬盈利嘅 2/3 即係 $4000 萬當做上半年盈利，咁你覺得啲廢嘅二世祖分析師會點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：佢哋可能會將 $4000 萬 &times; 2，即係當咗我今年盈利都係 $8000 萬啦，等於我好少冇賺少咁，假設股價冇變，都係維持 25 倍 P/E<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：冇錯，但𠵱個方法未必瞞到晒所有人，但至少瞞到大部份剩係睇表面盈利嘅人。老實講，大多數市值大嘅上市公司都唔會咁玩嘅，所以 Forecast P/E 對企鵝嗰類公司依然好有參考價值<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你𠵱個方法真係好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：講仆街點夠你星先生嚟呀，你呃盡政府錢，仲要「粉飾」報表<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：冇計啦，人在江湖。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：都話咗 HKNOIT，炒賣鳩吹造數先發大達<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後，窮狗繼續喺天橋底乞食，而星先生就繼續佢嘅創科（cap 水）之路。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUAybG4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUAybG4.jpg&h=16f90350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"6d54dd8dcede9a53c4892a4d0e751055bea7f2e1","tid":1949776,"uid":8941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:51:11.000Z","msg":"g持教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會教埋殘ga其他指標益下我呢d窮撚傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}